snippet.title: Treasure Hunters - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Add it to your wishlist on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2835460/Treasure_Hunters

Treasure Hunters is an intense CO-OP treasure-hunting game set in mysterious dungeons filled with puzzles, platforms, and deadly creatures where your goal is to find and steal the most valuable treasures.
